00:06:42.790 --> 00:06:47.860
But Look is a book that
deals in part with the US

00:06:47.860 --> 00:06:50.530
Department of Defense's
Dictionary of Military

00:06:50.530 --> 00:06:52.700
and Associated Terms.

00:06:52.700 --> 00:06:56.630
The US Department of Defense
has its own internal dictionary

00:06:56.630 --> 00:06:59.780
that aims to supplement
standard English dictionaries,

00:06:59.780 --> 00:07:02.660
amending the definitions
that we might find

00:07:02.660 --> 00:07:05.610
there to fit their context.

00:07:05.610 --> 00:07:08.840
So for example, the
word "look" itself

00:07:08.840 --> 00:07:12.730
has been redefined by the
Department of Defense to mean,

00:07:12.730 --> 00:07:16.160
in mine warfare, a period
during which a mine circuit is

00:07:16.160 --> 00:07:19.300
receptive of an influence.

00:07:19.300 --> 00:07:23.870
And the influence is
obviously the person

00:07:23.870 --> 00:07:25.970
that is stepping on the mine.

00:07:25.970 --> 00:07:28.760
So the definition
gives us a kind

00:07:28.760 --> 00:07:33.920
of example of the twisted
syntax, and the euphemism,

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:37.730
and everything that really goes
into creating a language that

00:07:37.730 --> 00:07:40.910
will allow for violence.

00:07:40.910 --> 00:07:48.230
And I have always been obsessed
with state-sponsored language,

00:07:48.230 --> 00:07:52.550
and how violence
against a bodies

00:07:52.550 --> 00:07:55.990
is premeditated in a
violence against language,

00:07:55.990 --> 00:07:58.790
how that intersects with
the role of the poet

00:07:58.790 --> 00:08:02.720
as a caretaker of
language if nothing else,

00:08:02.720 --> 00:08:06.800
and what it might mean to
make the language of the state

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:08.780
reckon with the
language of the lyric

00:08:08.780 --> 00:08:10.630
and the language of the self.

00:08:10.630 --> 00:08:14.400
And so that's where it
starts with this book.

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:18.590
Maybe to give us a sense
of the this DOD language,

00:08:18.590 --> 00:08:22.100
