Plymouth Rock, Rat Trap,

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:59.740
Cow Pens, Baghdad is Beautiful,
Backbreaker, Block Party,

00:08:59.740 --> 00:09:04.060
Swashbucklers, Swimmers,
Punisher, Beastmaster, Flea

00:09:04.060 --> 00:09:08.920
Flicker, Firecracker, Lightning
